Former casting bio:  
Rose Bochner is an LA-based NY transplant. She is a theatre director and writer and co-founder of the theatre company Shakespeare in the Square. She has studied at the American Shakespeare Center and has her BFA from NYU Tisch School of the Arts in Dramatic Writing. She has worked for Theatre for a New Audience, Disney Theatrical Group, and many others.

Rose is a Casting Associate at Telsey+Co Casting, working on various television shows, films, and plays.
